column1: Dkk1 = ( Mesp1 OR ( canWnt AND NOT exogen_BMP2_2 ) )
Fgf8 = ( NOT Mesp1 AND ( Foxc1/2 OR Tbx1 ) )
GATAs = ( Nkx2.5 OR Mesp1 OR Tbx5 )
Isl1 = ( Tbx1 OR Mesp1 OR Fgf8 OR ( canWnt AND exogen_canWnt_2 ) )
Nkx2.5 = ( ( Isl1 AND GATAs ) OR Tbx1 OR ( Mesp1 AND Dkk1 ) OR ( BMP2 AND GATAs ) OR Tbx5 )
Tbx5 = ( NOT ( Tbx1 OR canWnt ) AND ( Nkx2.5 OR Tbx5 OR Mesp1 ) AND NOT ( Dkk1 AND NOT ( Mesp1 OR Tbx5 ) ) )
